values:
&nbsp;Arrived at&nbsp;Earth following some glitch of an autobot. Had been eluding me and Sunburn for weeks.

Got the gnat in the end, but not before he managed to offline Sunburn.&nbsp;

On my own for now, but there seems like other decepticons have been here as well. Will have to try finding out what happened to Megatron.&nbsp;

Looks like Optimus Prime may be somewhere on the planet as well. Till I can track that one down though, I'll have to find entertainment where&nbsp;I can.

Disgusting little bags of flesh, the natives of this planet.
